BRIEFLY 
MCI to Pay Its First Dividend: MCI Communications Corp., the nation's 
second-largest long-distance phone company, will pay its first-ever dividend on 
common stock -- 5 cents per share -- starting next month, MCI Chairman William 
G. McGowan told shareholders at the company's annual meeting. MCI plans to pay 
a semiannual dividend of 5 cents. The dividend is payable June 11 to 
shareholders of record on May 21. 
